lead_paragraph: Belgium striker Michy Batshuayi is set to join Chelsea from Ligue 1 club Olympique Marseille, French sports daily L'Equipe reported on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Batshuayi to Join Chelsea, L'Equipe Reports
